There are rapid techniques available for

20
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:23,060
diagnosing RSV, imunoflorescence for
example.

21
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:26,900
And these rapid techniques tend to be even
more sensitive than cultures, again,

22
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:28,090
because the virus.

23
00:01:28,090 --> 00:01:29,140
Is, fickle.

24
